description: HomeAdvisor is looking for an experienced Front End Developer to join our Software Development team. In general, we are looking for someone who has experience working on public-facing web properties, and being part of a fast-paced, fun-loving team. Our environment can be fun, loose, iterative, and even chaotic at times - you've been warned. Code every day in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript/jQuery to make our site highly interactive. Integrate client-side code with web services, social platforms, and our Java-based infrastructure. Produce pixel-perfect layouts and sites from mock-ups provided by key business partners in Creative Design, UX/UI, and Product Development.

We’re looking for a Front-End Developer who can make an immediate impact building complex UIs that empower organizations to make intelligent decisions. You will work in the heart of downtown Denver within a small, agile team of developers and a UX Designer to deliver new features and improvements to our product. We are looking for experienced and passionate developers who want to make a difference while working in a startup environment that prioritizes our team and user community over unsustainable growth.
